<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Nill" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Nill,</orth> will not: <cit><quote>in scorn or friendship, n. I construe whether,</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 188" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 188</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>and, will you, n. you, I will marry you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 2.273" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 273</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it is, will he, n. he, he goes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 19</bibl></cit>. <emph>I n. relate,</emph> Per. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.0." default="NO" valid="yes">III Prol. 55</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>